Name *: InnovaGoods Multifunctional Eco Shower
Short Description:
Improve the condition of your skin with the new InnovaGoods Home Houseware Multifunction Ecoshower! Using this ecological shower produces numerous beneficial and relaxing effects on the skin, thanks to its mineral components. Germanium maintains and improves cellular health (an excellent transporter of oxygen molecules), while Tourmaline channels energy, transforming negative ions into positive, high-frequency ones. Both minerals are distributed throughout the shower hose and are frequently used in natural medicinal therapy. In this way, the water that flows through the hose reaches the skin with all of these beneficial properties.

  • Made of propylene
  • Contains Germanium and Tourmaline
  • Filters chlorine, impurities in the water, and improves the condition of your skin
  • Prevents infections and dermatitis, and activates the immune system
  • 8 types of water flow
  • Saves water by up to 65 % 
  • Approx. diameter: 8 cm
  • Approx. length: 25 cm
  • Packaging in 24 languages (English, French, Spanish, German, Italian, Portuguese, Dutch, Polish, Hungarian, Romanian, Danish, Swedish, Finnish, Lithuanian, Norwegian, Slovenian, Greek, Czech, Bulgarian, Croatian, Slovak, Estonian, Russian, Latvian)
